### Get all Rooms (for the authenticated user)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a Room
POST {{host}}/api/v1/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Project Room",
  "description": "A chat for our new project",
  "initialMemberIds": []
}

### Update Room Details
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/rooms/{{roomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Renamed Project Room",
  "description": "Updated room description for Project X",
  "initialMemberIds": []
}

### Get Room Members
GET {{host}}/api/v1/rooms/{{roomId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add Member to Room
POST {{host}}/api/v1/rooms/{{roomId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "memberId": "{{newMemberId}}",
  "role": "MEMBER"
}

### Get Room Messages
GET {{host}}/api/v1/rooms/{{roomId}}/messages?start=2025-01-01T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Send Message to Room
POST {{host}}/api/v1/rooms/{{roomId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello team, this is a test message.",
  "replyToMessageId": null,
  "timestamp": "2025-11-21T23:55:00Z"
}

### Websocket
WEBSOCKET {{host}}/ws/room
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}